Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.93,0:01:37.39,Hackadoll_Ep_Title,Text,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fscx90\fad(776,1)\pos(631,3)}Episódio 10: "Vamos Para Uma Fonte Termal!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.86,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,This is my first time at a hot spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:40.05,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.62,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Eu também.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:45.15,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Mal posso esperar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:52.62,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,We're getting into the hot spring \Nas a bonus from a job I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.62,0:01:54.25,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,You better be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:56.41,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Estamos indo na frente, #3-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.41,0:01:57.72,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,See you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:59.26,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Hey... Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.26,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:06.90,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:10.79,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,The water's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.77,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,And we have it all to ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.45,0:02:16.57,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,They're floating...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.44,0:02:21.09,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,So warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.85,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Get in more quietly, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:24.16,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,This is Heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.04,0:02:50.00,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Nothing beats a hot spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:51.45,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:54.33,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,I can die happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:56.70,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Hey, #4-chan, don't say such ominous things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.70,0:02:58.70,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,It's so good, it's criminal. Like murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:01.63,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Now, don't say that, or it might really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:15.59,bloodletter,,0,0,0,,Tonight, at midnight,\None of you will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.09,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.53,0:03:21.34,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,"Tonight, at midnight"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:23.22,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,"One of you"...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:25.11,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,"Will die."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.98,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.97,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,This is who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:39.91,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,This letter is an unmistakable \Ndeclaration of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:41.61,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:43.61,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,The killer is among us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:53.11,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,This is silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:54.29,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.04,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.51,0:03:59.00,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Anyone who takes off on their\Nown in the midst of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:02.31,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.97,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Inspector, wh-what's this white outline?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:07.92,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, as you may have guessed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.55,0:04:09.63,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,It's just for effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.08,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,I will begin interrogations now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.31,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Inspector! We shall assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.48,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Who are you girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.85,Hackadoll_Main,All,0,0,0,,Personal Entertainment AI, HackaDolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:23.13,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,You mean the ones that can \Nadvance a person in anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:24.77,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,All right. You're my assistants.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:26.03,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:29.70,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Wow, I've always wanted \Nto do something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.36,0:04:32.84,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Well? Are you ready to confess yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.23,0:04:35.95,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,If your poor mother saw you right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.71,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.07,0:04:39.67,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Make yourself comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.67,0:04:41.48,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Spit it out! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.48,0:04:43.00,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Here. Have some katsudon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.17,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:47.15,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Onde você estava no momento of the declaration?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:49.93,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,I took a bath, then I drank some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.64,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Leite? Isso é suspeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.01,0:04:57.00,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Chief. #4 has caused a lot \Nof trouble in the past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:05:00.47,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,So she has a record... Even more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.19,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Wait, no, no, no! Não fui eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.19,0:05:04.76,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Come on, guys, you were all with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:06.49,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,We were in the same bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.49,0:05:07.93,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,Ah! Ela tem razão!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.46,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Então ela tem um alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.18,0:05:12.66,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Todos têm um alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:13.76,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,Ou seja...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.58,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,That means?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.75,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,It's an unsolvable crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:19.96,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,It is not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.28,Hackadoll_Main,Owner,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:24.97,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,É o que parece.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:28.20,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Damn it! The killer won't strike while I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:28.97,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.31,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Hear me, killer! I see through your evil scheme!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.73,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Eu já vi esta faca em algum lugar antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.39,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Eu sei quem é o assassino!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.73,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,Shut up, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:47.86,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,Quit trying to play detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:49.25,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Keep it down a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.99,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Fine. Vocês não me deixam escolha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.74,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Shazam!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:54.70,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Tap, tap, tap, tap, and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:56.20,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.07,0:05:58.80,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:01.38,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,I blew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.38,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,#1-chan? Owner-san? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.22,0:06:06.22,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,Whoa... Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.87,0:06:10.12,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:12.14,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,sei quem é o assassino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.64,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:17.43,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,The letter was pinned in place with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.24,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.90,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,The killer is someone with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.51,0:06:24.40,Hackadoll_Main,Kurobane,0,0,0,,So who is the killer, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.68,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,O assassino é...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:31.41,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,The one who hid a knife in the changing room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.13,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,In other words, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.13,0:06:35.19,Hackadoll_Main,All,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.19,0:06:37.41,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Look at what I found in #4-chan's bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.79,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,#4-chan, I'm so disappointed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.54,0:06:43.74,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,At 11:58 pm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:46.33,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,Suspect apprehended!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.15,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,It's over! Let's take another bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.87,0:06:56.48,Hackadoll_Main,Owner,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. When did I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.81,0:07:00.72,Hackadoll_Main,Owner,0,0,0,,And where is that knife I asked \N#4-chan to get for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.77,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Faca?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.28,Hackadoll_Main,Owner,0,0,0,,Yes, the blade got nicked enquanto eu estava preparando o jantar,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.28,0:07:06.70,Hackadoll_Main,Owner,0,0,0,,então eu mandei a #4 pegar outra pra mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:08.93,Hackadoll_Main,#2,0,0,0,,Wait, so that knife was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:11.99,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,Huh? O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.99,0:07:14.63,Hackadoll_Main,Ishikawa,0,0,0,,#4, você tem o direito de permancer em silêncio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.76,Hackadoll_Main,#4,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:19.58,Hackadoll_Main,#1,0,0,0,,Apparently, o verdadeiro culpado foi pego algum tempo depois,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:22.02,Hackadoll_Main,,0,0,0,,from the fingerprints on the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.61,Hackadoll_Main,#3,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
